      "Text": "Security update for gnome-settings-daemon",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "\ngnome-settings-daemon was updated to fix a bug and a security issue:\n\nSecurity issue fixed:\n- CVE-2014-7300: The lockscreen can be bypassed with the Print Screen button.\n\nBug fixed:\n- Do not hide the cursor while there was no mutter running (bsc#905158).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
